27:48.000 --> 27:51.000
The group has calmed down.

27:51.000 --> 27:54.000
It can act outside of emotions.

27:54.000 --> 27:57.000
It can act constructively.

27:57.000 --> 28:00.000
Therefore, at this stage,

28:00.000 --> 28:03.000
