The stage of celebration of the victories of employees

29:23.000 --> 29:26.000
is related to the recognition of merits

29:26.000 --> 29:29.000
and achievements of employees.

29:29.000 --> 29:32.000
Therefore, do not forget to do this.

29:32.000 --> 29:35.000
And, of course, do not forget to celebrate.

29:35.000 --> 29:38.000
And, of course, do not forget to celebrate.

