32:15.000 --> 32:18.000
he will see this client and use my contact.

32:18.000 --> 32:21.000
And then go and prove where and why.

32:21.000 --> 32:24.000
Let's talk about trust.

32:24.000 --> 32:27.000
If you have lived through all the stages correctly,

32:27.000 --> 32:30.000
and your team has reached the stage of action,

32:30.000 --> 32:33.000
the key word is that trust is formed

32:33.000 --> 32:36.000
between employees

32:36.000 --> 32:39.000
towards each other and towards you as a leader.

