32:51.000 --> 32:54.000
If you remember,

32:54.000 --> 32:57.000
at the stage of formation it is total control,

32:57.000 --> 33:00.000
at the stage of storm it is step-by-step,

33:00.000 --> 33:03.000
at the stage of action it is control of the result.

33:03.000 --> 33:06.000
You trust your employees.

33:06.000 --> 33:09.000
You don't need to control the letters

33:09.000 --> 33:12.000
they wrote in the slide,

