33:30.000 --> 33:33.000
That is, you fully delegate the functions

33:33.000 --> 33:36.000
as a leader to your team.

33:36.000 --> 33:39.000
Again, because you trust them.

33:39.000 --> 33:42.000
So, dear listeners,

33:42.000 --> 33:45.000
