34:00.000 --> 34:03.000
Any relations

34:03.000 --> 34:06.000
go through certain periods of their development.

34:06.000 --> 34:09.000
Each period is very useful and very important.

34:10.000 --> 34:13.000
You don't need to worry

34:13.000 --> 34:16.000
