34:16.000 --> 34:19.000
You need to work with them.

34:19.000 --> 34:22.000
You don't need to worry when people in your team

34:22.000 --> 34:25.000
self-isolate and remain silent.

34:25.000 --> 34:28.000
You need to work with it.

34:28.000 --> 34:31.000
When you gather a new team and new people

34:31.000 --> 34:34.000
and your employees politely smile at each other,

34:34.000 --> 34:37.000
you shouldn't be proud that you are doing well.

34:38.000 --> 34:41.000
So, excessive leadership and insufficient leadership.

34:41.000 --> 34:44.000
These are two key problems

34:44.000 --> 34:47.000
that a leader faces

34:47.000 --> 34:50.000
when he tries to manage a team.

34:50.000 --> 34:53.000
There are consequences of excessive leadership

34:53.000 --> 34:56.000
and consequences of insufficient leadership.

34:56.000 --> 34:59.000
So, dear listeners,

34:59.000 --> 35:02.000
the consequences of insufficient leadership

35:02.000 --> 35:05.000
and the consequences of excessive leadership.

