I think each of you has a lot of experience

35:09.000 --> 35:12.000
in your professional life.

35:12.000 --> 35:15.000
Not only as a leader,

35:15.000 --> 35:18.000
but also as a member of the same team.

35:18.000 --> 35:21.000
What can happen to you

35:21.000 --> 35:24.000
if your leader,

35:24.000 --> 35:27.000
having misused the management style

35:27.000 --> 35:30.000
for the development of you and your team,

35:30.000 --> 35:33.000
uses the style of excessive leadership?

