You feel that you are not understood,

35:57.000 --> 36:00.000
that you are not listened to,

36:00.000 --> 36:03.000
and that you are not respected.

36:03.000 --> 36:06.000
But the main thing is that when you,

36:06.000 --> 36:09.000
