I told you that a person with high intelligence

01:03:01.000 --> 01:03:04.000
should be able to give assessments

01:03:04.000 --> 01:03:07.000
based on the situation.

01:03:07.000 --> 01:03:10.000
As soon as the team was filled with these roles,

